Put it above the fold.

128
00:12:58.529 --> 00:13:00.072
That's where we put it.

129
00:13:00.155 --> 00:13:02.616
- You're late again. Kent.
- Sorry. Perry.

130
00:13:03.283 --> 00:13:05.702
- Hey. loser.
- Hey. Steve.

131
00:13:06.161 --> 00:13:08.539
Hey. what do you got against adverbs. Kent?

132
00:13:08.622 --> 00:13:11.792
How are we supposed to know how we feel
when we read this malarkey?

133
00:13:12.167 --> 00:13:16.130
In sports writing. you learn
the sentence is the modifier.

134
