- Hey. Ma.
- "Ma!"

135
00:13:18.632 --> 00:13:20.592
Hey. Clark!

136
00:13:20.676 --> 00:13:23.345
Uh. me and Pa just wanted to call

137
00:13:23.428 --> 00:13:26.932
