140
00:13:31.520 --> 00:13:33.981
- Shut up. Steve.
- Like. uh. possum or chitlins...

141
00:13:34.064 --> 00:13:35.566
- What's that. Clark?
<i>- Sorry. Ma.</i>

142
00:13:35.649 --> 00:13:36.692
<i>I'm just in the middle of a big news day here.</i>

143
00:13:36.775 --> 00:13:37.776
What are chitlins?

144
00:13:37.860 --> 00:13:39.361
Chitlins are intestines.

145
00:13:39.444 --> 00:13:41.655
Thanks. Cat. You read this crud?

146
00:13:42.030 --> 00:13:43.532
I thought it was great. Clark.

147
00:13:44.366 --> 00:13:45.409
"Great"?

148
00:13:45.492 --> 00:13:47.619
Yeah! Front page! Big time!

149
00:13:47.703 --> 00:13:51.498
Well. we don't want to keep you. but. uh.

150
00:13:51.582 --> 00:13:53.709
wanted to say congrats.

151
00:13:53.792 --> 00:13:56.503
and tell you we're thinking 'bout you. Clark.

152
00:13:56.587 --> 00:13:59.840
- It's been a minute.
- Tell him don't be a stranger.

153
00:13:59.923 --> 00:14:02.217
Pa says. "Don't be a stranger."

154
00:14:02.301 --> 00:14:04.219
I. uh... Yeah. I heard him. Ma.

155
00:14:04.303 --> 00:14:05.929
Yeah. okay I gotta go. I gotta run.

156
00:14:06.430 --> 00:14:07.264
Yep. okay. Love you.

157
00:14:07.347 --> 00:14:10.893
So. this guy just flew into midtown
and started attacking people.

158
00:14:10.976 --> 00:14:12.728
