221
00:16:58.310 --> 00:17:00.562
They don't have...
And I have proof of this...

222
00:17:00.645 --> 00:17:03.148
a hidden headquarters in Antarctica

223
00:17:03.231 --> 00:17:05.859
that violates 12 international treaties.

224
00:17:05.942 --> 00:17:09.112
And they aren't aliens.

225
00:17:09.196 --> 00:17:11.865
Shouldn't all that be more than enough reason

226
00:17:11.948 --> 00:17:16.578
for PlanetWatch to at least bring
the Kryptonian in for questioning?

227
00:17:16.661 --> 00:17:18.705
Admittedly. I'm not comfortable

228
00:17:18.789 --> 00:17:22.667
