as dangerous as him on the loose.

229
00:17:22.751 --> 00:17:25.128
But the optics? Superman is popular.

230
00:17:25.212 --> 00:17:27.672
Less so every day. according to chatter online.

231
00:17:27.756 --> 00:17:30.634
Not to mention the potential risk
of failing to contain him.

232
00:17:30.717 --> 00:17:33.095
I assure you. Secretary. we can contain him.

233
00:17:33.178 --> 00:17:35.305
Yeah. they got this stuff. uh...

234
00:17:35.389 --> 00:17:36.681
What's this Kryptonite stuff called?

235
00:17:36.765 --> 00:17:39.476
- It's called Kryptonite.
- Well. it kills him. right?

236
00:17:39.559 --> 00:17:41.603
As far as we can ascertain.
there's none left on the planet.

237
00:17:41.686 --> 00:17:43.438
I have a workaround for that as well.

238
00:17:43.522 --> 00:17:45.190
You know what? It doesn't matter. Lex.

239
00:17:45.273 --> 00:17:47.234
Because without solid proof of malicious intent.

240
00:17:47.317 --> 00:17:48.610
it's just not worth the risk.

241
00:18:27.983 --> 00:18:29.568
What are you doing here?

242
00:18:29.651 --> 00:18:31.403
Three months ago. we had our first date.

243
00:18:31.486 --> 00:18:35.240
And so. to celebrate.
I am making you your favorite:

244
00:18:35.323 --> 00:18:36.741
breakfast for dinner.

245
00:18:36.825 --> 00:18:38.160
That's your favorite.

246
00:18:38.702 --> 00:18:39.786
You love breakfast.

247
00:18:39.870 --> 00:18:42.622
Yeah. for breakfast.
You love it for dinner.

248
00:19:02.100 --> 00:19:03.935
- What?
- It was very funny today.

249
00:19:04.019 --> 00:19:05.020
- What?
- It was hilarious.

250
00:19:05.103 --> 00:19:06.438
the little back-and-forth we had going.

251
00:19:06.521 --> 00:19:07.189
Mm.

