Hey. Pa.

1274
01:24:35.279 --> 01:24:38.074
Never seen you sleep that long.

1275
01:24:42.453 --> 01:24:47.542
Last week me. Ma. Hector and them.

1276
01:24:47.625 --> 01:24:50.920
we took a drive to Beerki's Burritos

1277
01:24:51.003 --> 01:24:52.380
down in Luttus.

1278
01:24:53.423 --> 01:24:56.342
Like the one that used to be out
by that old. uh. blue barn.

1279
01:24:56.426 --> 01:24:58.177
out on that I-9. you remember that?

1280
01:24:59.303 --> 01:25:03.474
- Mm-hmm.
- Burritos still just as good.

1281
01:25:08.187 --> 01:25:10.690
That Louanne.
she... she seems nice.

1282
01:25:11.357 --> 01:25:13.609
- It's Lois.
- Hmm?

1283
01:25:13.985 --> 01:25:15.069
Her name's Lois.

1284
01:25:15.736 --> 01:25:17.447
But yeah. she's... she's nice.

1285
01:25:19.615 --> 01:25:21.826
But you don't seem quite yourself.

1286
01:25:23.744 --> 01:25:26.456
Yeah. well. that message
that my parents sent with me.

1287
01:25:26.539 --> 01:25:28.624
I had never heard the second half before.

1288
01:25:29.417 --> 01:25:33.838
Well. I'd say what you wanted
that message to mean

1289
01:25:33.921 --> 01:25:35.798
says a whole lot more about you

1290
01:25:35.882 --> 01:25:38.926
than what anyone meant for it to mean.

1291
01:25:39.010 --> 01:25:40.595
Pa. you don't understand.

1292
01:25:44.098 --> 01:25:46.100
I'm not who I thought I was.

1293
01:25:51.355 --> 01:25:53.024
They sent me here to hurt people.

1294
01:25:53.983 --> 01:25:56.027
Parents aren't for telling their children

1295
01:25:56.110 --> 01:25:57.612
who they're supposed to be.

1296
01:25:59.113 --> 01:26:01.741
We are here to give y'all tools.

1297
01:26:01.824 --> 01:26:03.951
help you make fools of yourselves

1298
01:26:04.035 --> 01:26:06.621
all on your own.

1299
01:26:11.959 --> 01:26:12.793
No.

1300
01:26:15.004 --> 01:26:18.216
Your choices. Clark.

1301
01:26:19.050 --> 01:26:20.927
Your actions.

1302
01:26:22.929 --> 01:26:27.058
That's what makes you who you are.

1303
01:26:28.851 --> 01:26:30.394
I'll tell you something. Son.

1304
01:26:32.063 --> 01:26:33.481
I couldn't be...

1305
01:26:38.110 --> 01:26:40.530
more proud of you.

1306
01:26:49.830 --> 01:26:51.082
Ol' mush.

1307
01:26:51.791 --> 01:26:54.252
Clark. there's something
on the box you might wanna see.

1308
01:26:57.838 --> 01:26:59.215
<i>And over in Eastern Europe.</i>

1309
01:26:59.298 --> 01:27:01.050
<i>Boravian troops gather at the border.</i>

1310
01:27:01.133 --> 01:27:02.635
<i>seemingly mere minutes away</i>

1311
01:27:02.718 --> 01:27:04.971
<i>from invading Jarhanpur once again.</i>

1312
01:27:05.054 --> 01:27:06.889
<i>Now. nearby villagers are willing</i>

1313
01:27:06.973 --> 01:27:08.349
<i>and ready to defend their country.</i>

1314
01:27:08.432 --> 01:27:12.061
<i>despite the exponentially superior firepower</i>

1315
01:27:12.144 --> 01:27:14.021
<i>of the well-trained Boravian military.</i>

1316
01:27:29.120 --> 01:27:30.371
<i>The villagers cling onto</i>

1317
01:27:30.454 --> 01:27:31.998
<i>what little hope they have left.</i>

1318
01:27:32.290 --> 01:27:34.250
<i>as they're surrounded by the military.</i>

1319
01:27:34.625 --> 01:27:37.628
<i>Boravian president.
Vasil Ghurkos. says the invasion</i>

1320
01:27:37.712 --> 01:27:39.297
<i>is to protect the Jarhanpurian people</i>

1321
01:27:39.380 --> 01:27:40.756
<i>from a tyrannical government.</i>

1322
01:27:49.557 --> 01:27:52.435
Superman! Superman!

1323
01:27:52.518 --> 01:27:55.646
Superman! Superman!

1324
01:27:55.730 --> 01:27:57.898
Superman! Superman!

1325
01:27:57.982 --> 01:28:00.610
Superman! Superman!

1326
01:28:00.693 --> 01:28:02.987
Superman! Superman!

1327
01:28:03.070 --> 01:28:06.574
Superman! Superman! Superman!

1328
01:28:06.657 --> 01:28:10.786
<i>Superman! Superman! Superman!</i>

1329
01:28:13.164 --> 01:28:15.625
<i>Without Superman here to stop it this time.</i>

1330
01:28:15.708 --> 01:28:18.502
<i>the Jarhanpurians don't have much hope.</i>

1331
01:28:19.045 --> 01:28:21.881
I cleaned your boots.
I'll go get 'em for you.

1332
01:28:23.507 --> 01:28:24.508
<i>Superman.</i>

1333
01:28:24.592 --> 01:28:26.469
<i>We need you here in Metropolis now.</i>

1334
01:28:26.552 --> 01:28:27.928
I have to get to Boravia. Terrific.

1335
01:28:28.012 --> 01:28:30.264
There won't be a Boravia. or a Metropolis.

1336
01:28:30.348 --> 01:28:32.516
or a Planet Earth. if you don't get here soon.

1337
01:28:33.517 --> 01:28:35.186
This rift is about to tear into the city.

1338
01:28:35.269 --> 01:28:37.980
I can't stop it.
I need your help.

1339
01:28:40.733 --> 01:28:42.526
<i>All Metropolis citizens.</i>

1340
01:28:42.610 --> 01:28:45.279
<i>This is a mandatory evacuation.</i>

1341
01:28:45.363 --> 01:28:48.532
<i>Repeat: this evacuation
is not optional.</i>

1342
01:28:50.326 --> 01:28:52.828
<i>This is a mandatory evacuation.</i>

1343
01:28:52.912 --> 01:28:56.749
<i>Repeat:
this evacuation is not optional.</i>

1344
01:28:59.293 --> 01:29:01.837
<i>This is a mandatory evacuation.</i>

1345
01:29:08.969 --> 01:29:10.930
Yeah. I'm sure she's scared. but find her.

1346
01:29:11.013 --> 01:29:12.348
Yeah. we're all equally scared.

1347
01:29:13.099 --> 01:29:14.684
Come on. just put her on.

1348
01:29:15.393 --> 01:29:17.687
Please. Juanita. can you put
Persephone on the phone?

1349
01:29:18.396 --> 01:29:21.023
Yes. she will care! Cats
know the sound of your voice!

1350
01:29:21.107 --> 01:29:23.484
So. I was able to connect
with our contact at BodaBank.

1351
01:29:23.859 --> 01:29:25.277
Luthor's been selling arms to Ghurkos

1352
01:29:25.361 --> 01:29:27.613
for pennies on the dollar for years.

1353
01:29:27.697 --> 01:29:30.116
- Why. you ask?
- I do ask why.

1354
01:29:30.574 --> 01:29:34.078
He did it in exchange for half of Jarhanpur.

1355
01:29:34.161 --> 01:29:34.995
You're kidding.

1356
01:29:35.079 --> 01:29:37.331
At first. I thought Eve
was just sending me selfies.

1357
01:29:37.415 --> 01:29:39.417
But in the background of the shots

1358
01:29:39.500 --> 01:29:41.168
are maps. contracts.

1359
01:29:41.252 --> 01:29:43.713
all kinds of documents
chronicling Boravia's agreement

1360
01:29:43.796 --> 01:29:45.548
to cede half of the country to Lex Luthor

1361
01:29:45.631 --> 01:29:47.341
once the invasion is complete.

1362
01:29:47.425 --> 01:29:48.801
He wants to make himself king.

1363
01:29:49.301 --> 01:29:51.011
- King?
- King.

1364
01:29:51.470 --> 01:29:53.222
Should we really still be standing here?

1365
01:29:53.973 --> 01:29:56.100
Lois. you got that flying
saucer deal up on the roof?

1366
01:29:56.183 --> 01:29:58.936
- Yup.
- Grant. Troupe.

1367
01:29:59.019 --> 01:30:00.479
- Come on.
- Grab the board. Jimmy.

1368
01:30:00.563 --> 01:30:03.482
- How many does it hold?
- Five. or six. Six.

1369
01:30:03.566 --> 01:30:07.027
- Okay. Lombard. you too.
- Oh. thank you.

1370
01:30:07.111 --> 01:30:09.363
Why the hell would Lex want half a desert?

1371
01:30:09.447 --> 01:30:11.073
His cultish acolytes believe he's gonna create

1372
01:30:11.157 --> 01:30:13.117
a technologically advanced utopia.

1373
01:30:13.200 --> 01:30:13.951
Utopia?

1374
01:30:14.034 --> 01:30:15.119
There's a profit factor as well.

1375
01:30:15.202 --> 01:30:16.996
I mean. the petroleum deposits alone

1376
01:30:17.079 --> 01:30:18.706
are worth multiples of his investment.

1377
01:30:18.789 --> 01:30:20.040
Whatever his motives are.

1378
01:30:20.124 --> 01:30:21.417
we know Luthor did everything he could

1379
01:30:21.500 --> 01:30:22.877
to ruin Superman's reputation.

1380
01:30:22.960 --> 01:30:23.961
Eve's photos show

1381
01:30:24.044 --> 01:30:26.380
he was behind the whole Hammer of Boravia scam.

1382
01:30:26.464 --> 01:30:27.757
And all the bots stirring up

1383
01:30:27.840 --> 01:30:29.508
anti-Superman sentiment online.

1384
01:30:29.592 --> 01:30:32.428
Mr. Terrific believes
Luthor is also behind

1385
01:30:32.511 --> 01:30:34.930
the spreading rift between universes out there.

1386
01:30:35.014 --> 01:30:36.932
All of it seems to be geared
toward stopping Superman

1387
01:30:37.016 --> 01:30:39.226
from standing in the way
of the Boravian invasion. Chief.

1388
01:30:39.769 --> 01:30:42.605
Call me Perry. kid. Post the story. Fast.

1389
01:30:48.444 --> 01:30:50.112
- Buckle up. kids.
- Why don't I have a seat?

1390
01:30:50.196 --> 01:30:52.072
- Jimmy. will you transcribe?
- Uh-huh.

1391
01:30:58.871 --> 01:31:00.581
Oh. God!

1392
01:31:05.085 --> 01:31:07.463
The <i>Daily Planet</i> has
obtained exclusive information

1393
01:31:07.546 --> 01:31:09.590
proving that billionaire Lex Luthor is in league

1394
01:31:09.673 --> 01:31:11.967
with Boravian dictator. Vasil Ghurkos.

1395
01:31:19.892 --> 01:31:21.435
Clark. are you close?

1396
01:31:21.519 --> 01:31:23.020
It's about to hit Metropolis.

1397
01:31:23.103 --> 01:31:24.605
and my codes are not shutting it down.

1398
01:31:25.731 --> 01:31:26.816
Shit!

1399
01:31:44.416 --> 01:31:45.251
Uh-oh.

1400
01:31:53.008 --> 01:31:55.803
Lex! The rift is almost here!

1401
01:31:55.886 --> 01:31:57.429
So slow it down.

1402
01:31:57.513 --> 01:31:59.181
I can't unless I can put the code in to stop it.

1403
01:31:59.265 --> 01:32:00.599
Hold on a minute then.

1404
01:32:01.308 --> 01:32:03.769
- We gotta go. man!
- Otis!

1405
01:32:23.789 --> 01:32:26.125
Not sure where we're gonna land
when the world is gone.

1406
01:33:26.310 --> 01:33:27.353
There's a code to close the rift.

1407
01:33:27.436 --> 01:33:29.063
but it's too complicated to hack.

1408
01:33:29.355 --> 01:33:31.440
Luthor will have the code at LuthorCorp.

1409
01:33:31.523 --> 01:33:33.442
Just give me a minute.
I'll get Krypto. and we'll go...

1410
01:33:33.525 --> 01:33:35.152
You brought that dog. man?

1411
01:33:35.235 --> 01:33:38.447
Yeah. I didn't... didn't want him
killing my parents' cows.

1412
01:33:58.509 --> 01:33:59.301
Go on wide.

1413
01:33:59.385 --> 01:34:00.469
Wrong.
Focus on The Engineer.

1414
01:34:00.552 --> 01:34:02.388
- I'm on the alien. Larry.
- 7R.

1415
01:34:22.199 --> 01:34:23.492
It's not too late for either of you.

1416
01:34:23.575 --> 01:34:24.326
5A!

1417
01:34:24.410 --> 01:34:25.786
You don't have to do what Luthor...

1418
01:34:49.268 --> 01:34:50.728
<i>2X!</i>

1419
01:34:56.692 --> 01:34:58.444
Now. Angela. as planned.

1420
01:34:58.527 --> 01:35:01.113
fill his lungs and kill the son of a bitch.

1421
01:35:43.363 --> 01:35:45.824
Can't he hold his breath for over an hour?

1422
01:35:45.908 --> 01:35:47.701
Not without air in his lungs.

1423
01:35:47.785 --> 01:35:49.036
He'll be dead in minutes.

1424
01:35:49.119 --> 01:35:50.704
The nanites are suppressing his optic nerve.

1425
01:35:50.788 --> 01:35:52.998
Sight and X-ray vision
should be completely muted.

1426
01:35:53.082 --> 01:35:54.208
Lungs breached.

1427
01:36:00.172 --> 01:36:01.965
<i>Da?</i>

1428
01:36:52.432 --> 01:36:53.851
What's his game?

1429
01:36:55.185 --> 01:36:57.312
Using friction to get the nanites off?

1430
01:36:57.396 --> 01:36:58.981
Doesn't matter if he gets them off his face.

1431
01:36:59.064 --> 01:37:00.691
The nanites are still in his lungs.

1432
01:37:00.774 --> 01:37:02.609
Engineer. Ultraman. keep up.

1433
01:37:02.693 --> 01:37:04.361
<i>We're trying.</i>

1434
01:37:08.532 --> 01:37:10.450
- Maintain LOS.
- Yes. No shit. Larry.

1435
01:37:10.534 --> 01:37:11.285
Hurry.

1436
01:37:31.680 --> 01:37:32.931
He'll suffocate any minute.

1437
01:37:40.981 --> 01:37:42.941
Engineer. envelop him completely.

1438
01:38:09.593 --> 01:38:11.428
Wait! Wait. wait!
What is he doing?

1439
01:38:18.894 --> 01:38:22.356
I won't be able to sustain
the impact at this speed.

1440
01:38:24.441 --> 01:38:27.277
No. Angela. unsheathe!
He's the only one protected!

1441
01:38:44.169 --> 01:38:48.131
Entering the hole. Infrared. please?

1442
01:38:54.846 --> 01:38:56.473
Switch to night vision.

1443
01:39:00.394 --> 01:39:01.311
Whoa.

1444
01:39:29.006 --> 01:39:31.258
Her heart's still beating. but she's unconscious.

1445
01:39:31.758 --> 01:39:32.759
Call in the Raptors.

1446
01:40:00.412 --> 01:40:02.164
What the hell?

1447
01:40:02.247 --> 01:40:06.126
That's right. Cloning you
was relatively simple.

1448
01:40:06.209 --> 01:40:08.920
All it took was combing
the aftermath of your battles...

1449
01:40:09.004 --> 01:40:10.881
<i>until I located a strand of your hair.</i>

1450
01:40:10.964 --> 01:40:13.633
That's how you got into the Fortress.

1451
01:40:13.717 --> 01:40:14.885
You had my DNA.

1452
01:40:15.177 --> 01:40:18.096
Yes. but as is often the case with cloning.

1453
01:40:18.180 --> 01:40:19.431
the match was imperfect.

1454
01:40:19.514 --> 01:40:23.935
He might be even stupider
than you. If that's possible.

1455
01:40:24.019 --> 01:40:25.354
But easier to control.

1456
01:40:25.437 --> 01:40:27.522
- 3L.
- And stronger.

1457
01:40:28.857 --> 01:40:29.775
22K!

1458
01:40:32.736 --> 01:40:33.779
31D!

1459
01:40:34.738 --> 01:40:35.614
<i>2A!</i>

1460
01:40:36.740 --> 01:40:38.283
<i>5B! 5B!</i>

1461
01:40:39.159 --> 01:40:41.078
<i>6K! 9A!</i>

1462
01:40:42.788 --> 01:40:45.332
My brain will always win!

1463
01:40:45.415 --> 01:40:48.168
Brain beats brawn!

1464
01:41:39.928 --> 01:41:42.556
Superman. Superman.

1465
01:41:42.639 --> 01:41:45.267
Superman. Superman.

1466
01:41:50.730 --> 01:41:52.524
No matter what you do to me. Luthor.

1467
01:41:53.692 --> 01:41:55.485
your plans in Boravia won't work.

1468
01:41:55.569 --> 01:41:58.321
Oh. really? Why's that?

1469
01:41:58.697 --> 01:42:00.449
'Cause I called in some friends.

1470
01:42:01.032 --> 01:42:02.242
Mr. Luthor?

1471
01:42:03.577 --> 01:42:05.287
There is an anomaly at the border.

1472
01:42:18.008 --> 01:42:19.176
Sorry. kid.

1473
01:42:19.718 --> 01:42:21.052
Superman couldn't make it.

1474
01:42:22.012 --> 01:42:23.513
So you got an upgrade.

1475
01:43:17.651 --> 01:43:19.486
I know you won't kill me.

1476
01:43:20.028 --> 01:43:24.157
You are too delicate and weak. like Superman.

1477
01:43:24.241 --> 01:43:26.493
I'm not like Superman.

1478
01:43:34.000 --> 01:43:36.294
- It's perfect. Post it. kid.
- On it.

1479
01:43:42.717 --> 01:43:44.553
I think you overestimate the importance

1480
01:43:44.636 --> 01:43:47.097
of Jarhanpur to me. Superman.

1481
01:43:47.180 --> 01:43:48.682
<i>That was just a bonus.</i>

1482
01:43:49.349 --> 01:43:50.767
I'm not killing you

1483
01:43:50.850 --> 01:43:54.437
so the Boravian military conflict can proceed.

1484
01:43:54.938 --> 01:43:59.109
I created the Boravian military conflict

1485
01:43:59.192 --> 01:44:03.405
so I'd have an excuse to kill you!

1486
01:44:03.780 --> 01:44:05.532
<i>Once you involved yourself.</i>

1487
01:44:05.615 --> 01:44:06.992
<i>I knew I could easily get</i>

1488
01:44:07.075 --> 01:44:09.035
our government's support in nullifying you.

1489
01:44:09.619 --> 01:44:10.453
Why?

1490
01:44:11.037 --> 01:44:13.665
Because you're destroying us!

1491
01:44:13.748 --> 01:44:15.458
10Y. 13B.

1492
01:44:36.855 --> 01:44:38.440
You're driven by envy. Luthor.

1493
01:44:38.898 --> 01:44:42.694
- You couldn't be more obvious.
- No shit. I'm not dim.

1494
01:44:42.777 --> 01:44:45.905
I'm aware envy consumes my every waking moment.

1495
01:44:45.989 --> 01:44:46.948
13L.

1496
01:44:50.452 --> 01:44:53.163
I know when they mention Galileo or Einstein

1497
01:44:53.246 --> 01:44:55.165
or one of these other twits
in the same breath as me.

1498
01:44:55.248 --> 01:44:57.917
I feel a tide of vomit
burn the back of my throat.

1499
01:44:58.001 --> 01:44:59.294
But at least Galileo did something.

1500
01:44:59.377 --> 01:45:02.922
He wasn't some dopey Venusian
catapulted onto this planet.

1501
01:45:03.340 --> 01:45:06.217
just to have the world fawn over him.

1502
01:45:06.301 --> 01:45:11.097
because his strength illuminates
how weak we all really are.

1503
01:45:15.477 --> 01:45:18.730
So. my envy is a calling.

1504
01:45:18.813 --> 01:45:21.941
It is the sole hope for humanity.

1505
01:45:22.025 --> 01:45:26.780
because it is what has driven me
to annihilating you.

1506
01:45:26.863 --> 01:45:27.864
1A!

1507
01:45:28.198 --> 01:45:30.575
1A! 1A!

1508
01:45:30.659 --> 01:45:33.870
1A! 1A! 1A! 1A!

1509
01:45:33.953 --> 01:45:34.704
Yes.

1510
01:45:43.963 --> 01:45:47.550
Oh. what are you smirking at. you idiot?

1511
01:45:47.926 --> 01:45:51.888
Brain beats brawn.

1512
01:45:53.431 --> 01:45:54.432
Sorry. chum.

1513
01:46:11.241 --> 01:46:12.450
No. no. no! No!

1514
01:46:17.038 --> 01:46:20.208
You watch him through those?
Tell him what to do?

1515
01:46:28.174 --> 01:46:29.300
Krypto.

1516
01:46:30.802 --> 01:46:31.720
Get the toy.

1517
01:46:35.014 --> 01:46:37.517
Uh. thir-thirty-s...
Oh. the stupid dog!

1518
01:46:37.934 --> 01:46:39.227
- Uh...
- Charlie down!

1519
01:46:52.824 --> 01:46:54.743
- 12C! Aah!
- Delta down.

1520
01:47:00.790 --> 01:47:01.791
36B...

1521
01:47:02.917 --> 01:47:03.918
- No.
- Hotel down!

1522
01:47:11.718 --> 01:47:13.303
- No!
- Bravo down.

1523
01:47:13.386 --> 01:47:15.138
- Bravo down!
- I just said that. Larry!

1524
01:47:30.612 --> 01:47:31.863
Alpha down!

1525
01:47:33.782 --> 01:47:34.574
Lex.

1526
01:47:35.658 --> 01:47:37.285
The Raptors have arrived.

1527
01:47:42.749 --> 01:47:44.834
- Kill him!
- Good luck with that.

1528
01:48:49.816 --> 01:48:50.775
Hey!

1529
01:48:53.236 --> 01:48:56.447
This ain't playtime!
Quit messin' around!

1530
01:48:56.531 --> 01:48:58.491
We have to get to Luthor to stop the rift.

1531
01:48:58.575 --> 01:48:59.742
I'm not messing around.

1532
01:48:59.826 --> 01:49:01.369
I'm doing important stuff.

1533
01:49:03.955 --> 01:49:05.957
It's gonna reach Bakerline any minute.

1534
01:49:06.416 --> 01:49:07.750
There are people there.

1535
01:49:15.133 --> 01:49:16.634
- We have to go.
- We'll never make it in time.

1536
01:49:16.718 --> 01:49:18.094
- It's almost here.
- We have to try. Come on.

1537
01:49:22.348 --> 01:49:24.017
Lex!

1538
01:49:25.393 --> 01:49:26.686
I'm closing the freakin' rift.

1539
01:49:26.769 --> 01:49:29.397
No! They chose him!
Let them die!

1540
01:49:29.480 --> 01:49:31.441
- We'll close it from the bunker
- What?

1541
01:49:31.524 --> 01:49:33.192
before it gets to a city I care about.

1542
01:49:35.695 --> 01:49:36.946
Open the portal!

1543
01:49:41.910 --> 01:49:43.661
Wrap it up. Let's go.

1544
01:49:44.412 --> 01:49:45.955
Safety first. people.

1545
01:49:58.176 --> 01:50:00.887
Hey. Hey. The code
to close the rift is in here.

1546
01:50:01.721 --> 01:50:03.723
- I can help.
- I don't need your help.

1547
01:50:04.307 --> 01:50:06.225
I'm goddamn Mr. Terrific.

1548
01:50:07.435 --> 01:50:10.313
You piece of shit alien!

1549
01:50:11.522 --> 01:50:14.108
That is where you've always
been wrong about me. Lex.

1550
01:50:15.193 --> 01:50:16.945
I'm as human as anyone.

1551
01:50:17.028 --> 01:50:19.656
I love. I... I get scared.

1552
01:50:19.739 --> 01:50:22.408
I wake up every morning. and
despite not knowing what to do.

1553
01:50:22.492 --> 01:50:24.202
I put one foot in front of the other.

1554
01:50:24.285 --> 01:50:26.537
and I try to make the best choices I can.

1555
01:50:26.621 --> 01:50:28.373
I screw up all the time.

1556
01:50:28.456 --> 01:50:30.333
But that is being human.

1557
01:50:31.626 --> 01:50:33.461
And that's my greatest strength.

1558
01:50:34.879 --> 01:50:38.925
And someday I hope. for the sake of the world.

1559
01:50:39.008 --> 01:50:41.010
you understand that it's yours too.

1560
01:50:41.094 --> 01:50:43.554
Oh. that's beautiful.

1561
01:50:43.638 --> 01:50:46.808
But none of this matters. you patronizing clown.

1562
01:50:46.891 --> 01:50:50.603
The government gave me the authority to kill you.

1563
01:50:50.687 --> 01:50:52.480
If not today. then tomor...

1564
01:50:52.563 --> 01:50:53.523
Ahh!

1565
01:50:58.611 --> 01:50:59.821
No. no. no!

1566
01:50:59.904 --> 01:51:02.281
Oh. my... Stop.
Krypto. put him down.

1567
01:51:05.076 --> 01:51:06.452
Krypto. drop him!

1568
01:51:06.536 --> 01:51:07.996
Krypto. drop him! Drop him!

1569
01:51:13.084 --> 01:51:14.836
Dude.

1570
01:51:20.508 --> 01:51:21.759
Got it.

1571
01:51:36.315 --> 01:51:38.067
Yes!

1572
01:51:47.160 --> 01:51:49.328
Mmm.

1573
01:51:50.079 --> 01:51:51.581
- Lex.
- What?

1574
01:51:52.331 --> 01:51:54.208
<i>Well. this just in.
An absolute bombshell</i>

1575
01:51:54.292 --> 01:51:55.626
<i>from the</i> Daily Planet.

1576
01:51:55.710 --> 01:51:57.879
<i>Billionaire Lex Luthor aligning himself</i>

1577
01:51:57.962 --> 01:52:00.256
<i>with a foreign entity. believe it or not.</i>

1578
01:52:00.339 --> 01:52:01.674
<i>Luthor has been giving them</i>

1579
01:52:01.758 --> 01:52:04.260
<i>billions and billions of
dollars' worth of free weapons...</i>

1580
01:52:04.343 --> 01:52:07.346
<i>Lex Luthor has been working
covertly with Vasil Ghurkos</i>

1581
01:52:07.430 --> 01:52:08.765
<i>and the Boravian government</i>

1582
01:52:08.848 --> 01:52:11.601
<i>to overthrow the country of Jarhanpur.</i>

1583
01:52:11.684 --> 01:52:13.311
<i>Luthor has been giving them billions...</i>

1584
01:52:13.394 --> 01:52:15.605
<i>We've had Luthor on this show many times.</i>

1585
01:52:16.314 --> 01:52:18.191
<i>Little did we know. he was a traitor.</i>

1586
01:52:21.903 --> 01:52:22.862
<i>Seems like the one thing</i>

1587
01:52:22.945 --> 01:52:25.656
<i>conservatives and liberals can finally agree on</i>

1588
01:52:25.740 --> 01:52:27.116
<i>is that Lex Luthor sucks.</i>

1589
01:52:27.533 --> 01:52:30.870
<i>The whole world has turned against Superman.</i>

1590
01:52:30.953 --> 01:52:33.873
<i>and we all owe him an enormous apology.</i>

1591
01:52:34.290 --> 01:52:38.377
<i>He is. of course. the hero
we always thought he was.</i>

1592
01:53:09.200 --> 01:53:11.786
Thank you! Thank you!

1593
01:53:17.333 --> 01:53:18.543
That was sick.

1594
01:53:19.252 --> 01:53:21.587
Guy. maybe he should join the group.

1595
01:53:21.671 --> 01:53:23.172
Please.

1596
01:53:23.256 --> 01:53:25.967
I mean. no offense. but that
creepy mug is what you want

1597
01:53:26.050 --> 01:53:27.969
representing the Justice Gang?

1598
01:53:28.052 --> 01:53:29.053
Justice Gang?

1599
01:53:29.929 --> 01:53:31.222
That's a cool name.

1600
01:53:32.265 --> 01:53:33.015
You're in.

1601
01:53:36.060 --> 01:53:37.145
Come on!

1602
01:53:40.565 --> 01:53:41.566
Glad you're not concerned

1603
01:53:41.649 --> 01:53:42.900
