1604
01:53:43.693 --> 01:53:45.945
'Cause now they're the ones making the rules.

1605
01:53:57.999 --> 01:53:59.500
Everyone file. This way. please.

1606
01:53:59.584 --> 01:54:00.668
Easy!

1607
01:54:00.751 --> 01:54:03.588
- Fleurette!
- Mom!

1608
01:54:06.757 --> 01:54:07.800
