Miss Lane.

1613
01:55:07.526 --> 01:55:09.695
Oh. hi.

1614
01:55:10.196 --> 01:55:12.031
I thought I might give you an interview.

1615
01:55:12.782 --> 01:55:15.284
I could fill you in
on all of the behind-the-scenes.

1616
01:55:15.368 --> 01:55:16.244
Sure.

1617
01:55:17.119 --> 01:55:18.621
I think that would be...

1618
01:55:20.248 --> 01:55:20.998
great.

1619
01:55:22.833 --> 01:55:24.043
Um...

1620
01:55:24.126 --> 01:55:25.169
How about over here?

1621
01:55:25.544 --> 01:55:26.545
For an interview.

1622
01:55:59.996 --> 01:56:00.830
Hey.

1623
01:56:04.208 --> 01:56:05.418
I love you. too.

1624
01:56:32.862 --> 01:56:34.322
How long have they been hooking up?

1625
01:56:34.405 --> 01:56:35.656
About three months. I think.

1626
01:56:40.828 --> 01:56:42.997
Got this place cleaned up pretty good.

1627
01:56:43.080 --> 01:56:45.041
Cleaned yourself up pretty good. too.

1628
01:56:45.124 --> 01:56:46.917
