1631
01:56:51.756 --> 01:56:54.050
Well. Four's a name.

1632
01:56:54.550 --> 01:56:55.801
So is Gary.

1633
01:56:59.055 --> 01:57:00.556
Aw. shoot.

1634
01:57:00.639 --> 01:57:02.683
Sir. I think your cousin has returned.

1635
01:57:05.144 --> 01:57:08.981
- Yup.
- What the hell. dude?

1636
01:57:09.982 --> 01:57:11.609
Why did you move the door?

1637
01:57:11.692 --> 01:57:14.236
- I didn't move the door.
- Where is my dog?

1638
01:57:21.827 --> 01:57:24.246
Okay. well. this is why he has behavioral issues.

1639
01:57:24.330 --> 01:57:25.623
No boundaries.

1640
01:57:29.085 --> 01:57:31.045
- It's not healthy. is it?
- Mm-mmm.

1641
01:57:40.513 --> 01:57:41.680
Come on.

1642
01:57:41.764 --> 01:57:43.891
Thanks for watching him. bitch.

1643
01:57:47.269 --> 01:57:49.772
She likes to go and party on other planets.

1644
01:57:49.855 --> 01:57:51.899
- Planets with red suns.
- Oh.

1645
01:57:51.982 --> 01:57:53.275
Because of our metabolism.

1646
01:57:53.359 --> 01:57:55.861
we can't get drunk on a planet with a yellow sun.

1647
01:57:55.945 --> 01:57:58.322
If I had any emotional capacity whatsoever.

1648
01:57:58.406 --> 01:58:00.366
I'd be concerned about her partying.

1649
01:58:00.658 --> 01:58:01.409
Yeah.

1650
01:58:01.742 --> 01:58:05.121
Superman. would you like to see
the footage of your parents?

1651
01:58:05.204 --> 01:58:07.665
- He finds it soothing.
- Oh!

1652
01:58:08.082 --> 01:58:09.917
Yeah. Gary. that'd be nice.

1653
01:58:16.966 --> 01:58:17.883
<i>Everything you see.</i>

1654
01:58:17.967 --> 01:58:19.301
<i>you're seeing for the first time.</i>

1655
01:58:26.684 --> 01:58:28.144
<i>All of this is for you.</i>

1656
01:58:31.522 --> 01:58:32.440
<i>Clark.</i>

1657
