What do you want me to do?

1665
02:08:43.216 --> 02:08:45.093
Do you want me to take it apart
and put it back together?

1666
02:08:45.177 --> 02:08:46.636
No. no. no. no. I was just...

1667
02:08:48.555 --> 02:08:49.473
You just what?

1668
02:08:52.059 --> 02:08:53.935
Hey. man. I'm sorry.
I didn't mean to bum you out.

1669
02:08:55.854 --> 02:08:57.230
I shouldn't have brought it up.

1670
02:08:58.440 --> 02:09:01.068
Darn it. I can be such a jerk sometimes.
